c: 24
v: 43
t: "Akuboni na ukuba uAllâh Uqhuba amafu ngobunono, Aze awahlanganise, Aphinde Awenze imfumba eyalekeneyo, uze ubone imvula iphuma ivela kuwo. Yaye Yena Uthoba esibhakabhakeni, iintaba (zamafu) ekukho kuzo isichotho, Abethe ngaso lowo Athande (ukumbetha) Asishenxise kuye nabani na lowo Athande (ukusishenxisa) kuye. Ukulanyaza kombane aso kuphantse kuthabathe ukubona kwamehlo (abo)"